00292 void CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdaterTest::testMultiData1()
00293 {
00294         CreateReferenceFile1();
00295 
00296     vector<ColumnInfo> cols;
00297         CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdater upd;
00298     ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData e;
00299         upd.Initialize(TEST1_FILE);
00300 
00301     e.call = 11;
00302     e.confidence = 111.0f;
00303         upd.UpdateMultiData(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, e);
00304 
00305     e.call = 22;
00306     e.confidence = 222.0f;
00307         upd.UpdateMultiData(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, e);
00308 
00309         CHPMultiDataData data;
00310         CHPMultiDataFileReader reader;
00311         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.SetFilename(TEST1_FILE));
00312         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.Read(data));
00313         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 4);
00314 
00315     data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, e);
00316         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "1");
00317         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 11);
00318     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 111.0f, 0.000001f);
00319         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, e);
00320         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "2");
00321         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 2);
00322         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 20.0f, 0.000001f);
00323         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 2, e);
00324         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "3");
00325         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 22);
00326         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 222.0f, 0.000001f);
00327         data.GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 3, e);
00328         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "4");
00329         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 4);
00330         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.confidence, 40.0f, 0.000001f);
00331 }
